sections.text:
The Department shall adopt regulations that:

(1)    establish a registration form for the initial and renewal registration of a land professional;

(2)    set fees for the issuance of an initial registration and for a registration renewal;

(3)    provide for the assignment of a registration number and the issuance of a registration certificate to each registered land professional; and

(4)    establish any other requirements and procedures necessary to implement this title.
